    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Happy St. Patrick\u2019s Day! Great time in downtown Cleveland today.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2034033441302581611",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-17T22:25:37+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "We back the blue. Great visit to FOP Lodge 15 in Medina County.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2034012406280847431",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-17T21:02:02+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Amazing wife, incredible mother, world-class surgeon, &amp; the next First Lady of Ohio. Inspiring healthcare professionals across Ohio, 5 weeks after giving birth to our third child. Couldn\u2019t be more proud. \u2764\ufe0f\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2033206303502504161",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T15:38:52+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Lower costs. Bigger paychecks. Better schools.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2032924173149024713",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T20:57:47+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "A St. X grad walks into a bar in Cincinnati on St. Patrick\u2019s Day weekend &amp; this is how it goes. Love it every time. \ud83c\udf40\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2032920067265208789",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T20:41:28+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Great meeting last night with dentists &amp; healthcare providers across the state. Triple-header of events today in Sharonville, West Chester, &amp; Columbus. Back to full speed post-baby!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2032810659151491338",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T13:26:43+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Our deepest condolences to the families of these great American heroes. Very sad to hear this news.\n\n\nGovernor Mike DeWine (@GovMikeDeWine)\n\nI have been advised by Ohio's Adjutant General that three of the six servicemembers killed during the air refueling mission in Iraq were Ohioans deployed with the\u00a0Ohio\u00a0Air National Guard's 121st\u00a0Air Refueling Wing. Fran and I are deeply saddened by this news and offer our sincere condolences to their families.\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/GovMikeDeWine/status/20",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2032598371962335320",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T23:23:10+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Enjoyed spending time with President Trump in my hometown of Cincinnati today. Great conversations with local workers about delivering lower costs, bigger paychecks, and better schools. We\u2019ll do our part in Ohio. \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2031869789380206737",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T23:08:02+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The leading edge of our country begins at its center, right here in Ohio. It was an honor to keynote the opening of the Chabad House at Ohio State this weekend.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2027408412804595924",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-27T15:40:07+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I ran into a student who I met at the 2024 OSU - Penn State game, who told me back then that he was a Democrat before we had a chat. It was nice to see him again in a different context last week.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2027075273280340405",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-26T17:36:21+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The best way to bring down the cost of homes is to increase the supply &amp; cutting the regulations that get in the way. That shouldn\u2019t be controversial, it\u2019s common sense.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2027031706444939272",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-26T14:43:13+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The President did a great job last night in laying out sensible energy policies to bring down electric bills for everyday Americans. In Ohio, I\u2019ll ensure that hyperscalers pay for their own energy usage, and we\u2019ll produce more energy too, to bring down costs for consumers.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2026666332767555750",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T14:31:22+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "It\u2019s the 250th anniversary of the Declaration of Independence, and I\u2019m grateful to hear tonight from a Commander-in-Chief who is actually proud of our country. Can\u2019t deny that.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2026479110164451727",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T02:07:24+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The first part of addressing affordability is to undo the inflation crisis created by government overgrowth under Biden, but the other half is to increase wealth\u2014by putting more money back in Americans\u2019 pockets.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2026478431790354695",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T02:04:42+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "vivek-ramaswamy",
      "voiceName": "Vivek Ramaswamy",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Lower property taxes, lower electric bills, lower housing costs.\n\nBigger paychecks, better schools, more wealth creation.\n\nComing soon to Ohio.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/VivekGRamaswamy/status/2026451354798170427",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-25T00:17:07+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
